Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同跟随我到地狱的尽头吧！
